room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by Escape Room Alexandria in Alexandria (MN)
review: What a blast! We did the Bank Heist, was challenging and such a rush! Definitely want to take another crack at that safe!

room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by Escape Room Alexandria in Alexandria (MN)
review: Escape room Alexandria MN is a MUST DO when visiting Alex! Our group did the vault themed room and almost escaped, we loved it so much that we did another room right after! There were so many amazing props, exciting moments and great puzzles. Great job!
